About REQ Power Hour

Join RepEquity Thursday for the REQ Power Hour Tech Talk and developer happy hour. RepEquity tech team will be speaking for an hour about our tech after which we invite people in tech and tech adjacent fields to have a drink with us! The REQ Power Hour is part of DC FemTech's Tour de Code - a month long coding extravaganza of DC tech! Contact Jessica Bell for more details. Schedule, projects, lectures, and information will be posted soon - so check back soon!
